Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界在撒谎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.80,0:00:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可杀人 不可偷盗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.21,0:00:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可欺瞒 不可奸淫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.77,0:00:14.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都是谎言 诓骗而已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.38,0:00:17.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想被杀 不想被盗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.89,0:00:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才以正义伦理等谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.48,0:00:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保护弱小的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.24,0:00:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原始的真理乃是弱肉强食
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.28,0:00:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吞噬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.54,0:00:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人的财富 权力 乃至世界本身
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.85,0:00:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯有我布里塔尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.58,0:00:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能击碎世界的谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.22,0:00:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带来真实
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.38,0:00:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All Hail Britannia
