Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.38,0:02:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,0)}被舍弃的 面具
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.42,0:02:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像在做噩梦 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.45,0:02:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.99,0:02:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了吗 昨天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.30,0:02:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…我说什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.46,0:02:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜…娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.22,0:02:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥什么也没说 什么也没
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.30,0:02:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.96,0:02:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉所期望的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.83,0:03:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉所选择的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.81,0:03:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而在那里 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.57,0:03:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO是阻碍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.08,0:03:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉的人身安全有保障
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.02,0:03:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有布里塔尼亚正规军 还有朱雀在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.72,0:03:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然作为敌人他们无比棘手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.25,0:03:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但棘手也正体现了这保障的可信度
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.16,0:03:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 就像我曾经期望过的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.35,0:03:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使没有我保护 也已…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.04,0:03:27.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看你看 听说这个寺庙是一千年前建的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.72,0:03:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别提这个了 你看到水枪了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.12,0:03:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明准备了大家的份的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.51,0:03:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.82,0:03:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,网子 蜡烛 假发 烟花
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.16,0:03:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有铃鼓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.64,0:03:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…我们是去修学旅行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.33,0:03:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包在我身上 我是第二次了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.61,0:03:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 鲁鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.07,0:03:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像没什么精神
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.57,0:03:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.11,0:03:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是太期待修学旅行 兴奋得没睡着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.43,0:03:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…其实就是这么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.84,0:04:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁鲁真像个小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.42,0:04:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,11区新总督即将发表就任致辞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.19,0:04:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请全体同学到礼堂集合
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.65,0:04:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.85,0:04:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是布里塔尼亚第87皇位继承人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.22,0:04:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉·V·布里塔尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.48,0:04:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代替日前殉职的卡拉雷斯公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.04,0:04:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出任本届11区总督
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.14,0:04:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我双目失明且腿脚不便
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.13,0:04:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总督？那样的小女孩？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.86,0:04:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.72,0:04:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还请各位多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.05,0:04:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还说多多关照…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.88,0:04:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄得我都乱了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.34,0:04:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然匆忙 有一事希望大家能协助于我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.19,0:04:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打算重建日本行政特区
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.40,0:04:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.31,0:04:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟说出这种犯忌的话来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.74,0:05:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在日本特区
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.20,0:05:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布里塔尼亚人和属区人民将受到平等对待
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.57,0:05:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,11区人可以重获日本人之名
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.27,0:05:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她刚才说日本人…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.19,0:05:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又想欺骗我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.75,0:05:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枢木朱雀也在一起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.70,0:05:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他也一样是日本人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.79,0:05:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是杀戮公主的骑士啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.36,0:05:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出卖ZERO的叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.20,0:05:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然过去在日本特区曾发生过不幸的错误
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.57,0:05:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我认为其目标并没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.26,0:05:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平等 温柔的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.98,0:05:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑色骑士团的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.06,0:05:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也请务必加入日本特区
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.24,0:05:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还来？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.45,0:05:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今还…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.97,0:05:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承认彼此的错误 一定可以重来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.10,0:05:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我坚信这点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.83,0:05:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓我一跳 娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.39,0:05:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会说出重建日本特区…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.08,0:06:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀 尤菲皇姐想做的事是正确的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.01,0:06:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 错的不是尤菲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.24,0:06:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换乘急行列车的乘客
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.09,0:06:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请在下车后到站台对面的3号线等待
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.61,0:06:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一站可换乘千京线
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.75,0:06:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,470)\fad(0,700)}各站停车将在5号站台…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.20,0:06:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,470)}已经不需要了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.49,0:06:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是ZERO 还是我的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.02,0:06:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个总督也和杀戮公主尤菲米娅一样嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.37,0:06:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确 日本人谁也不会参加吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.60,0:06:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用甜言蜜语把人引出来 然后赶尽杀绝？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.38,0:06:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少瞧不起人了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.59,0:07:00.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 今后怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.40,0:07:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是跟布里塔尼亚决战了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.39,0:07:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的Knightmare可只剩下红莲一架了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.47,0:07:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说 只要ZERO…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.87,0:07:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.77,0:07:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神乐耶殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.94,0:07:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玉城先生说得没错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.30,0:07:14.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但怎么不见ZERO大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.76,0:07:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新婚妻子特地赶来的说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.34,0:07:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在中华联邦时他也连封信都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.07,0:07:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是出轨了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.27,0:07:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别胡说八道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.05,0:07:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人 他是骗人的 神乐耶殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.14,0:07:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.12,0:07:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓英雄爱美人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.93,0:07:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鉴于成年男子的生理状况…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.36,0:07:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.05,0:07:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮大忙了 你比看起来更成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.47,0:07:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不在的时候 感谢你陪伴他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.67,0:07:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不足挂齿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.20,0:07:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 卡莲小姐也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.02,0:07:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.15,0:07:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,支持ZERO大人的三位…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.41,0:08:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是三宫女呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.41,0:08:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}注：三宫女是女儿节用来装饰的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.11,0:08:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宫女？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.28,0:08:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.78,0:08:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀君呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.02,0:08:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说要追寻黑色骑士团 出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.17,0:08:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精密检查还没结束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.84,0:08:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点还是老样子 他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.25,0:08:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了完成Conquista…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.16,0:08:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.48,0:08:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑麦面包加黄姜 日本砂糖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.39,0:08:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混合后再加芥末酱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.81,0:08:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是老样子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.51,0:08:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我至今为止所作所为 都是为了娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.48,0:08:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.65,0:08:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是布里塔尼亚第87皇位继承人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.95,0:08:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉·V·布里塔尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.91,0:08:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代替日前殉职的卡拉雷斯公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.19,0:09:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么 小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.62,0:09:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.29,0:09:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉或许已察觉了我的谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.91,0:09:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但即使如此 她还是说要继承尤菲的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.87,0:09:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是为了这 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.79,0:09:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了先给钱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.67,0:09:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦死了 穷光蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.76,0:09:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,败家犬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.71,0:09:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 你们不也一样是11区人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.19,0:09:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要这个 就拿钱来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.20,0:09:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布里塔尼亚人？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.39,0:09:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.32,0:09:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本人吃日本人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.85,0:09:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还是以布里塔尼亚人走狗的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.92,0:09:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说日本人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.20,0:09:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁要布里塔尼亚人同情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.95,0:09:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是11区人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.57,0:10:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,区区学生少管人家做生意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.58,0:10:07.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是自愿为我所用的 学生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.02,0:10:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别碰我 贱民
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.12,0:10:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.46,0:10:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我做俯卧撑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.49,0:10:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.42,0:10:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科尔恰克先生 您做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.98,0:10:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1 2…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.08,0:10:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.74,0:10:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下蹲运动 嗥叫 拍手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.40,0:10:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1 2 1 2…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.91,0:10:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不回这儿来也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.96,0:10:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说 他活着更重要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.51,0:10:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能…光是不当ZERO那很简单
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.20,0:10:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也不是多浪漫的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.37,0:11:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这样下去 黑色骑士团就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.43,0:11:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「为娜娜莉而存在的ZERO」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.56,0:11:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁路修这么说呢 玛莉安娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.33,0:11:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁路修呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.39,0:11:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道 他到底想什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.45,0:11:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然来了这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.47,0:11:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是ZERO…你开始的地方
Comment: 0,0:00:00.04,0:00:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTB------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.25,0:11:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁路修 我对你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.18,0:11:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.16,0:11:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Refrain
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.66,0:11:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡莲也知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.39,0:11:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以靠这个回到怀念的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.92,0:11:59.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别胡闹了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.47,0:12:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是失败了一次又怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.71,0:12:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再想作战计划挽回不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.34,0:12:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像往常一样下命令给我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.38,0:12:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开Knightmare？还是诱饵搜查？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.09,0:12:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么我都听你的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.89,0:12:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.51,0:12:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安慰我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.93,0:12:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用女人才能做到的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.40,0:12:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.91,0:12:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作点 鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.88,0:12:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在你是ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.88,0:12:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给了我们梦想 就要负责任
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.82,0:12:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.19,0:12:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就把我们骗到底啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.82,0:12:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次一定要把完美的ZERO…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.38,0:12:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演到底啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.27,0:13:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗洛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.87,0:13:29.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的任务是监视我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.36,0:13:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.78,0:13:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 忘了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.79,0:13:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些都是痛苦的重负
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.43,0:13:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO是 黑色骑士团是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.64,0:13:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.59,0:13:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 娜娜莉是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.76,0:13:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是为了娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.59,0:13:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO消失的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.97,0:13:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,11区就能获得和平
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.13,0:13:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥也恢复到普通学生的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.70,0:13:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸福生活就是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.14,0:13:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.13,0:13:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追求幸福 有什么不对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.65,0:13:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会伤害到任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.31,0:13:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还可以将一切归零
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.09,0:14:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 只有我不会去任何地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.86,0:14:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远和哥哥在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.52,0:14:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.27,0:14:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为何志愿提出
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.52,0:14:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出任ZERO复活后的11区总督
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.99,0:14:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前一直受到哥哥的保护
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.25,0:14:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在虽然他行踪不明
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.86,0:14:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他一定还在关注着我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.56,0:14:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我要做出
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.88,0:14:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会给哥哥丢脸的选择
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.25,0:14:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很重哦 那面具
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.68,0:14:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅仅是日本人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.51,0:14:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还需要肩负整个世界的觉悟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.53,0:14:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是必须有人…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.84,0:14:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是布里塔尼亚军
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.91,0:14:50.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵舰所属及航路 与申报有异
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.27,0:14:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请停船
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.98,0:14:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在将进行强行临检
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.09,0:14:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被发现了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.31,0:14:58.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.50,0:14:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们将等待十分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.83,0:15:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此之前所有乘员解除武装
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.81,0:15:03.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到甲板上站好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.03,0:15:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 大家都去修学旅行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.00,0:15:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要追上去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.19,0:15:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不了 空无一人的鸟笼正适合现在的我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.21,0:15:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.73,0:15:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回来了 鲁鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.12,0:15:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁路修也来放吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.74,0:15:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文化祭用剩下的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.64,0:15:39.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？修学旅行呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.88,0:15:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是就我们去了 你会哭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.90,0:15:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅行这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.56,0:15:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关键不在于去哪里 而是跟谁一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.43,0:15:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.14,0:15:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.39,0:15:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.71,0:15:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说能实现愿望 就做了试试
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.05,0:16:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过怎么也想不起是跟谁学的了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.56,0:16:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你许了什么愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.20,0:16:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经实现了 一点点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.32,0:16:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和大家一起放烟花
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.71,0:16:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.83,0:16:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼娜 卡莲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.12,0:16:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.13,0:16:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有鲁路修和罗洛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.92,0:16:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为只折了一只 所以只实现了鲁鲁这份
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.75,0:16:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记得以前曾跟娜娜莉 朱雀说过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.40,0:16:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若幸福有形态的话 那会是怎样的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.34,0:16:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是了 就像朱雀说的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.15,0:16:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许幸福就像玻璃一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.42,0:16:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为平时从未察觉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.34,0:16:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但它确实存在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.27,0:16:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,证据就是 稍微改变看的角度
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.55,0:16:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玻璃就会映照出光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.93,0:17:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比任何东西更雄辩地主张自己的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.29,0:17:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说折一千只这种纸鹤 就能实现愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.41,0:17:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉想许什么愿望？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.57,0:17:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望有一个温柔的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.95,0:17:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.12,0:17:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温柔的世界就近在咫尺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.12,0:17:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使为虚伪的记忆所玷污
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.59,0:17:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却更显出透明的琉璃色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.73,0:17:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直 永远
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.45,0:17:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.16,0:17:24.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁鲁？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.90,0:17:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你哭什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.79,0:17:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被我们的友情所感动了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.39,0:17:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也有可爱的一面嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.86,0:17:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦 怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.38,0:17:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.63,0:17:41.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再来这里一起放烟花吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.83,0:17:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定 一定要再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.83,0:17:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和大家一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.70,0:17:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 我的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.22,0:17:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不仅是为了娜娜莉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.24,0:17:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.44,0:17:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.53,0:18:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了 爆破油轮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.61,0:18:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使敌方声纳失效
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.26,0:18:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下俯配平30度 急速潜航
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.71,0:18:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO的联络呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.03,0:18:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依然断绝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.34,0:18:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该又打算潜入海底逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.68,0:18:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出动PortmanII
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.14,0:18:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以被动模式确认
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.43,0:18:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从动力音判断应该是水中型
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.38,0:18:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降低深度 被发现就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.04,0:18:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ASROC（反潜导弹）发射
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.19,0:18:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要惊慌 这是无的放矢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.73,0:18:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以θ地点为中心张开包围网
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.16,0:18:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定能把敌人逼出来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.17,0:19:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.08,0:19:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰内各部进水
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.55,0:19:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤堂先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.58,0:19:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一移动会被对方捕捉到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.33,0:19:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.32,0:19:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.90,0:19:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.42,0:19:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Q1 听到吗 Q1
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.82,0:19:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这声音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.30,0:19:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.37,0:19:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下俯配平50度
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.07,0:19:22.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向地点L14急速潜航
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.99,0:19:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶上了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.89,0:19:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 太迟啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.03,0:19:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续投放深水炸弹 保持包围网
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.92,0:19:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝向正面 鱼雷全弹发射
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.56,0:19:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用定时信管设40秒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.50,0:19:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正面？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.14,0:19:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有敌人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.72,0:19:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射试试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.40,0:19:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了相信他 还有别的办法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.01,0:19:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,设定信管后 全弹发射
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.90,0:19:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认鱼雷发射音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.33,0:19:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕捉到敌方位置
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.17,0:19:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人在地点L14
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.99,0:20:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集中攻击 等它浮上我来捕捉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.58,0:20:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnsimsun\fs16\pos(320,442)\b}火蜥蜴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.58,0:20:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnsimsun\fs16\pos(565,442)}蓝海豚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.58,0:20:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Salamander呼叫BlueDolphin
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.34,0:20:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向定点改变发射角度
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.42,0:20:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Portman布阵区域 传送
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.26,0:20:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.34,0:20:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,网眼不大 别设错目标了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.33,0:20:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是Salamander 已确认
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.03,0:20:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标设定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.02,0:20:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炸弹投射管 旋转
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.66,0:20:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射准备
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.84,0:20:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,固定锚后
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.97,0:20:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各员 准备承受冲击
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.94,0:20:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空气？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.02,0:20:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 甲烷水合物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.60,0:20:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.36,0:20:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浮力…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.30,0:20:58.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枢木卿 水泡…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.01,0:21:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水泡？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.90,0:21:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转舵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.76,0:21:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 即将翻船
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.79,0:21:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.93,0:21:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海底涌起巨大的水泡？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.25,0:21:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.49,0:21:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀 这不是叫援军就能解决的问题了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.35,0:21:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集合幸存的部队
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.08,0:21:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将黑色骑士团…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.90,0:21:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.95,0:21:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO往这边来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.29,0:21:32.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.96,0:21:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你的回答吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.88,0:21:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.79,0:21:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开枪就是违抗君令
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.66,0:21:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.34,0:21:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我决定接受娜娜莉总督的提案
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.07,0:21:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 就是日本特区的提案
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.49,0:21:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.68,0:21:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是投降了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.34,0:21:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.05,0:21:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.23,0:21:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO下令
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.79,0:21:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑色骑士团全员
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.88,0:22:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加入日本特区！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------NEXT------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.49,0:23:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许你确实正面带笑容 正在享受
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.82,0:23:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 那并非真实
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.51,0:23:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隐藏在你那笑容背后的悲剧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.10,0:23:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我一人知道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.04,0:23:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若只有一人知道真相 拥有救赎的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.01,0:23:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 那么我理当反抗的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.75,0:23:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是名为和平的统治
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.88,0:24:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔑视 欺瞒我们
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.27,0:24:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将我们视作玩物的系统
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.33,0:24:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以ZERO的名义…


